{"tid":238943,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樂視未找數！】樂視體育被入稟 追收107萬廣告費","createTime":"2017-05-11T10:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T19:03:52.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8cd5c55332ef33fe5e83e274606ff2bed92c695","tid":238943,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/11/184008_aa678a703baf1414fbce7e22426c258b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F11%2F184008_aa678a703baf1414fbce7e22426c258b.jpg&h=9dcac89d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據提交香港高等法院的傳票，Polarline Development稱其為樂視體育文化產業發展（香港）有限公司，提供了展示型廣告服務。<br />\n<br />\n文件指，樂視去年8-9月，預訂了香港七個站點的展示標識。Polarline指，工作已經完成，但雖幾經催討，樂視體育一直沒有與其結算，兩筆總計107萬港元的款項。Polarline入稟要求索償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56680212&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56680212%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=31e108f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56680212%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170511&h=ad6c4e33\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56680212&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170511</a>"},{"pid":"596cb5d26313eb95950c5c6767cb02f5d6cb8a74","tid":238943,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:43:14.000Z","msg":"呢間野點解仲未有人清佢盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfc1d95eb4759dfe4641791af90fd2581e8ba26","tid":238943,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T19:03:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"